[06/10/2018 00:47:51] <font color="#00ffff">Ven.</font>
[06/10/2018 00:48:02] <font color="#00ffff">¿Venís mucho aquí?</font>
[06/10/2018 00:48:06] <font color="#ffff00">A veces.</font>
