[06/10/2018 11:14:04] <font color="#ffffff">Sí.</font>
[06/10/2018 11:14:04] <font color="#ffffff">-Los trenes de frenaban a mano.</font>
[06/10/2018 11:14:05] <font color="#ffff00">¿Cómo se frenaba a mano?</font>
