[06/10/2018 15:32:17] <font color="#ffffff">en 1970:</font>
[06/10/2018 15:32:22] <font color="#ffffff">Ni siquiera yo he dicho nunca algo...</font>
[06/10/2018 15:32:22] <font color="#ffffff">tan militante.</font>
