[06/10/2018 18:58:56] <font color="#ffffff">¡Eh, Lazarito bonito mío!</font>
[06/10/2018 18:58:59] <font color="#ffffff">-...matando...</font>
[06/10/2018 18:58:59] <font color="#ffffff">Me va a matar.</font>
