[06/10/2018 23:55:19] <font color="#0000ff">bailando se cubre</font>
[06/10/2018 23:55:20] <font color="#0000ff">tras un diván.</font>
[06/10/2018 23:55:20] <font color="#0000ff">¡Ay!</font>
[06/10/2018 23:55:23] <font color="#0000ff">Vaya, era la reina</font>
[06/10/2018 23:55:23] <font color="#0000ff">que a mí me picó.</font>
